---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping Policy">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Shipping Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>ROAM Systems delivers across the United Kingdom. Please review our shipping information below.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Build & Delivery Times</h2>
        <p>Our products are precision-crafted to order. Build time is typically 2-4 weeks depending on the complexity of your order and current demand. Once dispatched, delivery is usually within 3-5 working days.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Delivery Costs</h2>
        <p>Delivery costs vary based on order size, weight, and your delivery location. We will provide an accurate delivery quote when we contact you to confirm your order.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Tracking</h2>
        <p>Once your order has been dispatched, we will provide you with tracking information so you can monitor the delivery of your order.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">International Shipping</h2>
        <p>We currently only deliver within the United Kingdom. If you are based outside the UK, please contact us to discuss collection arrangements or alternative shipping options.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Delivery Issues</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or there are any issues with your delivery, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:sales@roamsystems.co.uk" class="text-roam-orange hover:underline">sales@roamsystems.co.uk</a> and we will resolve the issue promptly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
